17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 19 O.S. 2021, Section 130.1, as
19 amended by Section 1, Chapter 86, O.S.L. 2023 (19 O.S. Supp. 2025,
20 Section 130.1), is amended to read as follows:
21 Section 130.1. There is hereby re-created, to continue until
22 July 1, 2026 2031, in accordance with the provisions of the Oklahoma
23 Sunset Law, the Commission on County Government Personnel Education
24 and Training, hereinafter called the "Commission". The Commission
